{"word":"G5526 - χορτάζω - chortázō - khor-tad'-zo - Feed","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">χορτάζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">chortázō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">khor-tad'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Feed</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - திருப்தியடை"},{"paragraph":"1. to feed with herbs, grass, hay, to fill or satisfy with food, to fatten"},{"paragraph":"2. to fulfill or satisfy the desire of anyone"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5528 - χόρτος - chórtos - khor'-tos/5528\">G5528</a>; to <i>fodder</i>, that is, (genitive case) to <i>gorge</i> (<i>supply food</i> in abundance): - feed, fill, satisfy.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G5526/5526\">G5526</a>, <a href=\"#/G5527/5527\">G5527</a>, <a href=\"#/G5528/5528\">G5528</a>"}]}